{"tid":1969460,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"索羅斯、巴菲特等高手損失逾兆元","createTime":"2020-04-12T12:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T19:11:45.000Z","uid":18795,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2b54c0c87b5cfae52bddff38ee77fdf47e0e5de6","tid":1969460,"uid":18795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:20:43.000Z","msg":"「股神級」的喬治索羅斯（George Soros）以及華倫巴菲特（Warren Buffett）正是最有代表性的兩位！這兩位剛剛在八月「慶祝」七十八歲生日的老先生（索羅斯比巴菲特早生了十八天），最近煩惱可多著呢！兩位大師生日相近、投資哲學剛好相反，但是今年的操作，都遇到史無前例的亂流。索羅斯光買三支股票就賠掉新台幣二百億元，巴菲特投資公司淨值一口氣跌掉新台幣一兆元，兩位大師都說，這是他們從未見過的災難！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.businesstoday.com.tw/article/category/80392/post/200809250038/索羅斯、巴菲特等高手損失逾兆元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fcategory%2F80392%2Fpost%2F200809250038%2F%E7%B4%A2%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E3%80%81%E5%B7%B4%E8%8F%B2%E7%89%B9%E7%AD%89%E9%AB%98%E6%89%8B%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%E9%80%BE%E5%85%86%E5%85%83&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=6e347fb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.businesstoday.com.tw/article/category/80392/post/200809250038/索羅斯、巴菲特等高手損失逾兆元</a>"},{"pid":"022552733bcc74d415970c7df88b4d0d6f186745","tid":1969460,"uid":18795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10b06c9f6736fcf57df1bb309f357dd7bcee570","tid":1969460,"uid":84081,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:22:35.000Z","msg":"2008年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d523afb88d58a656306ea01264e959f8a8efee","tid":1969460,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:23:41.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cla